        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/n/2acd7d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-02-09T13:39:39.242Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I have received messages inside the app asking me to enter my 64 digit recovery code. This seems really odd, because there should be no reason for the app to ask this. This kind of information would, of course, be very valuable to an outside attacker.</p>\n<p>I have read reports of phishing attempts by malicious actors to gain access to signal users\u2019 messages. So: Is this a phishing attempt?</p>\n<p>Screenshots in German attached.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/f/4/f4a7b86cf73c4cb37371e36a2991e327749e8b57.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/f4a7b86cf73c4cb37371e36a2991e327749e8b57\" title=\"IMG_1512\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/4/f4a7b86cf73c4cb37371e36a2991e327749e8b57_2_358x500.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_1512\" data-base62-sha1=\"yUjQd5WffQ2Q4NEFG42gDlZOhYH\" width=\"358\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/4/f4a7b86cf73c4cb37371e36a2991e327749e8b57_2_358x500.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/4/f4a7b86cf73c4cb37371e36a2991e327749e8b57_2_537x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/4/f4a7b86cf73c4cb37371e36a2991e327749e8b57_2_716x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"28292D\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_1512</span><span class=\"informations\">817\u00d71138 71.6 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/2/d/2dcc373fbf723819ae04301f85b6b7311e509208.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/2dcc373fbf723819ae04301f85b6b7311e509208\" title=\"IMG_1511\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/d/2dcc373fbf723819ae04301f85b6b7311e509208_2_690x249.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_1511\" data-base62-sha1=\"6x911zJw4mT8p0DCHWtLN19l45W\" width=\"690\" height=\"249\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/d/2dcc373fbf723819ae04301f85b6b7311e509208_2_690x249.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/2/d/2dcc373fbf723819ae04301f85b6b7311e509208.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/2/d/2dcc373fbf723819ae04301f85b6b7311e509208.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"424244\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_1511</span><span class=\"informations\">828\u00d7299 46.2 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
