      {
        "id": 284252,
        "name": "",
        "username": "nickster",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/n/2acd7d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-02-09T17:04:24.866Z",
        "cooked": "<p>It looks very much like the PIN reminder which you can set to get in the settings.</p>\n<p>However, the Signal websites says, Signal will never ask for verification codes:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://support.signal.org/hc/en-us/articles/9932566320410-Staying-Safe-from-Phishing-Scams-and-Impersonation\" class=\"onebox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://support.signal.org/hc/en-us/articles/9932566320410-Staying-Safe-from-Phishing-Scams-and-Impersonation</a></p>\n<p>Hence, I have the worry that the Signal app has been hacked in a serious way to distribute these legimate looking messages.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/8/d/8dea04ed0f178b493baba2f3da3c8b9955de6675.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/8dea04ed0f178b493baba2f3da3c8b9955de6675\" title=\"Bildschirmfoto 2026-02-09 um 18.02.22\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/8/d/8dea04ed0f178b493baba2f3da3c8b9955de6675_2_690x52.png\" alt=\"Bildschirmfoto 2026-02-09 um 18.02.22\" data-base62-sha1=\"kfqHQERPSY1uctPf5WRl8rQaXad\" width=\"690\" height=\"52\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/8/d/8dea04ed0f178b493baba2f3da3c8b9955de6675_2_690x52.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/8/d/8dea04ed0f178b493baba2f3da3c8b9955de6675_2_1035x78.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/8/d/8dea04ed0f178b493baba2f3da3c8b9955de6675_2_1380x104.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"F0F0F0\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Bildschirmfoto 2026-02-09 um 18.02.22</span><span class=\"informations\">1386\u00d7106 8.32 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
