        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/n/2acd7d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-02-09T20:43:03.042Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thank you for your explanation, which seems reasonable.</p>\n<p>I would suggest Signal changes their support page where they claim they \u201cwill never ask for verification codes, recovery keys, or payment details\u201d. That is a bit confusing.</p>",
